org.cpsolver.instructor.model

Class TeachingAssignment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.model.Value<TeachingRequest.Variable,TeachingAssignment>
      • org.cpsolver.instructor.model.TeachingAssignment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TeachingAssignment>, AssignmentComparable<TeachingAssignment,TeachingRequest.Variable,TeachingAssignment>

    public class TeachingAssignment
extends Value<TeachingRequest.Variable,TeachingAssignment>
    Teaching assignment. An assignment of an instructor to a teaching request (a set of sections of a course). A teaching assignment also contains the value of attribute, instructor, course, and time preferences.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Instructor Sectioning)
